                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The funeral of King <persName>George VI</persName> was held in London on February
                    15. Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_ACHESONDG1">Acheson</persName> was
                    the principal representative of President Truman. <persName
                        corresp="#p_ACHESONDG1">Acheson</persName>’s personal recollections of the
                    day are to be found in <persName corresp="#p_ACHESONDG1">Acheson</persName>, <hi
                        rend="italic">Present at the Creation</hi>, pages 610–614.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
